  "title": "Administrator to CEO/ACADEMIC DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p>Job Position: Administrator to CEO/ACADEMIC DIRECTOR</p><p>Workplace: Executive Counselling and Training Academy</p><p>Address: 2 Bukit Merah Central #03-07 S(159835)</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description</p><p>Work directly with CEO/ACADEMIC DIRECTOR and provide administrative support</p><p><br /></p><p>Responsibilities</p><p>1. Provide administrative support</p><p>2. Reply emails independently</p><p>3. Prepare PowerPoint slides</p><p>4. Maintain management files</p><p>5. Provide ad-hoc support<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Skills and Knowledge</p><p>1. English proficiency</p><p>2. Clear verbal and written communications skills</p><p>3. Tech-savvy (Google Suite, Microsoft Office, etc.)</p><p>4. PowerPoint savvy <br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Attributes and Requirements</p><p>1. Warm Personality</p><p>2. Flexibility in work styles</p><p>3. Supportive and relational</p><p>4. Positive attitude and mature</p><p>5. Strong interpersonal skills</p><p>6. Track progress of tasks given and do follow up</p><p>7. Work experience in supporting Directors and above</p><p>8. Resilient and Professional</p><p>9. Able to handle fast pace dynamic work environment</p><p>10. Organised and detail-oriented</p><p>11. Able to handle confidential information with discretion</p><p>12. Able to accept phone calls after office hours <br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Work Hours</p><p>1. 4-day work week (8.30am to 6.00pm)</p><p>2. One Saturday a month and taketime-off on weekdays<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Salary and Benefits</p><p>1. Monthly Gross Salary: $3.4k - $3.6k</p><p>2. 14-day Annual leave</p><p>3. Medical and accident insurance</p><p>4. $750 Medical claim per annum ($75 per claim for registered GP Clinics)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
